          "parameters": {
            "color": 6,
            "width": 336,
            "height": 416,
            "content": "## 📊 Keephub Weekly Task Report\n\nFetches all tasks for an org unit from the past week, \ngets their progress, and sends a formatted Slack summary.\n\n**Setup:**\n1. Add your Keephub Login credential\n2. Add your Keephub Bearer credential\n3. Set your orgunit ID in \"Get Tasks by Orgunit\"\n4. Set your Slack channel in the Slack node\n\nRuns automatically every Monday at 9:00am.\n"
